engChrName: Wh... L-Let go of me!
engSearchText: Wh... L-Let go of me!
jpnChrName: ちょっ…… アンタたち、放しなさいよ～！？
jpnSearchText:
ちょっ……
アンタたち、放しなさいよ～！？

engChrName: It came from over there!
engSearchText: It came from over there!
jpnChrName: 向こうの方からです！
jpnSearchText: 向こうの方からです！

engChrName: That voice... It figures.
engSearchText: That voice... It figures.
jpnChrName: この声……やっぱりか。
jpnSearchText: この声……やっぱりか。

engChrName: Hnngh!
engSearchText: Hnngh!
jpnChrName: むうウン……！
jpnSearchText: <C2>むうウン……！

engChrName: Haaaah!
engSearchText: Haaaah!
jpnChrName: ハアあっ……！
jpnSearchText: <C2>ハアあっ……！

engChrName: L-Let me GO, alre—wait! I know you!
engSearchText: L-Let me GO, alre—wait! I know you!
jpnChrName: だ、だからいい加減に ──ってアンタたち……！？
jpnSearchText:
だ、だからいい加減に
──ってアンタたち……！？

engChrName: Miss Grimcat!
engSearchText: Miss Grimcat!
jpnChrName: グリムキャッツさん……！？
jpnSearchText: グリムキャッツさん……！？

engChrName: Sorry. We interrupt your fun?
engSearchText: Sorry. We interrupt your fun?
jpnChrName: ……ワリ、お楽しみだったか？
jpnSearchText: ……ワリ、お楽しみだったか？

engChrName: (Wh-Why is my heart beating so fast all of a sudden?)
engSearchText:
(Wh-Why is my heart beating so fast all of
a sudden?)
jpnChrName: （な、なんだかドキドキします。）
jpnSearchText: （な、なんだかドキドキします。）

engChrName: Do I LOOK like I'm having fun?! Now hurry up and give me a hand!
engSearchText:
Do I LOOK like I'm having fun?! Now hurry up and
give me a hand!
jpnChrName: プレイじゃないからっ……！ いいから早く助けなさいっ！
jpnSearchText:
プレイじゃないからっ……！
いいから早く助けなさいっ！

engChrName: Guess we got no choice.
engSearchText: Guess we got no choice.
jpnChrName: 仕方ねえな……！
jpnSearchText: 仕方ねえな……！

engChrName: You owe us one now—or two, if we count the night before last.
engSearchText:
You owe us one now—or two, if we count the night
before last.
jpnChrName: これで貸し一つ──いや、 おとといの夜も入れて二つか？
jpnSearchText:
これで貸し一つ──いや、
おとといの夜も入れて二つか？

engChrName: Shut up! Just make with the punching and knock 'em out!
engSearchText:
Shut up! Just make with the punching and knock
'em out!
jpnChrName: うるさいわねっ！ ──このまま無力化するわよ！
jpnSearchText:
うるさいわねっ！
──このまま無力化するわよ！

engChrName: Oof... It's not easy, knocking people out without really hurting them.
engSearchText:
Oof... It's not easy, knocking people out without
really hurting them.
jpnChrName: ふう、傷つけないように 気絶させるのも難しいわね……
jpnSearchText:
ふう、傷つけないように
気絶させるのも難しいわね……

engChrName: What took you guys so long, anyway?!
engSearchText: What took you guys so long, anyway?!
jpnChrName: ──てゆうか、遅いじゃないっ！
jpnSearchText: ──てゆうか、遅いじゃないっ！

engChrName: You understand we didn't come to save you in the first place, right?
engSearchText:
You understand we didn't come to save you in the
first place, right?
jpnChrName: 別にお前さんを助けにきた わけじゃねえんだが……
jpnSearchText:
別にお前さんを助けにきた
わけじゃねえんだが……

engChrName: She IS one of the people we're here to help, though. Technically.
engSearchText:
She IS one of the people we're here to help, though.
Technically.
jpnChrName: いや、厳密に言えば コイツも保護対象なんじゃね？
jpnSearchText:
いや、厳密に言えば
コイツも保護対象なんじゃね？

engChrName: Oh, you're right... We're glad you're safe!
engSearchText: Oh, you're right... We're glad you're safe!
jpnChrName: あ、確かに…… よくご無事でしたねっ。
jpnSearchText:
あ、確かに……
よくご無事でしたねっ。

engChrName: Well, uhh...I-I have NO idea what you're talking about!
engSearchText:
Well, uhh...I-I have NO idea what you're
talking about!
jpnChrName: う、うぐ…… な、なんのことぉ～？
jpnSearchText:
う、うぐ……
な、なんのことぉ～？

engChrName: (...Why does this seem familiar somehow?)
engSearchText: (...Why does this seem familiar somehow?)
jpnChrName: （……考えてみれば   このノリ、どこかで……）
jpnSearchText:
（……考えてみれば
このノリ、どこかで……）

engChrName: (I see now...)
engSearchText: (I see now...)
jpnChrName: （成程……もしかして。）
jpnSearchText: （成程……もしかして。）

engChrName: Either way, you still owe us. So you can pay us back with a little friendly info swapping.
engSearchText:
Either way, you still owe us. So you can pay us back
with a little friendly info swapping.
jpnChrName: ──とにかく貸しは貸しだ。 まずは情報交換といこうぜ。
jpnSearchText:
──とにかく貸しは貸しだ。
まずは情報交換といこうぜ。

engChrName: So the orbal hookahs were what made all of this possible...
engSearchText:
So the orbal hookahs were what made all of
this possible...
jpnChrName: 導力シーシャを吸った人が…… そういうことだったのね。
jpnSearchText:
導力シーシャを吸った人が……
そういうことだったのね。

engChrName: Those scumbags have sent everyone who's ever smoked one into a frenzy.
engSearchText:
Those scumbags have sent everyone who's ever
smoked one into a frenzy.
jpnChrName: それをあの連中が 無理矢理暴走させたってワケか……
jpnSearchText:
それをあの連中が
無理矢理暴走させたってワケか……

engChrName: Sounds like Almata had people in the hotel after all.
engSearchText: Sounds like Almata had people in the hotel after all.
jpnChrName: 《アルマータ》── ホテルに紛れ込んでやがったとはな。
jpnSearchText:
《アルマータ》──
ホテルに紛れ込んでやがったとはな。

engChrName: And sure enough, they brought the device we're looking for along with them.
engSearchText:
And sure enough, they brought the device we're
looking for along with them.
jpnChrName: そしてやっぱり あれを持ち込んでいやがったか。
jpnSearchText:
そしてやっぱり
あれを持ち込んでいやがったか。

engChrName: Judging by the color, it's likely the one that angelic doll carried off.
engSearchText:
Judging by the color, it's likely the one that angelic
doll carried off.
jpnChrName: ……はい、色からして あの人形が持ち去ったものかと。
jpnSearchText:
……はい、色からして
あの人形が持ち去ったものかと。

engChrName: It must have been delivered to them after the fact.
engSearchText: It must have been delivered to them after the fact.
jpnChrName: 多分あの後、 アルマータに渡したんだと思います。
jpnSearchText:
多分あの後、
アルマータに渡したんだと思います。

engChrName: That girl did say something about how she and that doll had already played their part.
engSearchText:
That girl did say something about how she and that
doll had already played their part.
jpnChrName: 自分たちの役目はここまで── 確かにそう言っていましたね。
jpnSearchText:
自分たちの役目はここまで──
確かにそう言っていましたね。

engChrName: Hmm... We've met Melchior before, but who could the man in the coat be?
engSearchText:
Hmm... We've met Melchior before, but who could
the man in the coat be?
jpnChrName: で、ですがあのメルキオルはともかく “コートの男”っていうのは……
jpnSearchText:
で、ですがあのメルキオルはともかく
“コートの男”っていうのは……

engChrName: That's a good freaking question. I've never seen him before, either.
engSearchText:
That's a good freaking question. I've never seen him
before, either.
jpnChrName: さあ……残念だけど あたしには見覚えは無かったわ。
jpnSearchText:
さあ……残念だけど
あたしには見覚えは無かったわ。

engChrName: The prince and Naje bought most of us time to escape by fighting against them, but I ended up getting separated from everyone.
engSearchText:
The prince and Naje bought most of us time to
escape by fighting against them, but I ended up
getting separated from everyone.
jpnChrName: 殿下とナージェさんが連中とやり合う隙に 他の人たちは逃がしたんだけど……
jpnSearchText:
殿下とナージェさんが連中とやり合う隙に
他の人たちは逃がしたんだけど……

engChrName: I think Nina and Mr. Gotti are still there, though...
engSearchText: I think Nina and Mr. Gotti are still there, though...
jpnChrName: 結局、はぐれちゃって…… ニナや監督たちも多分まだあの場所に……
jpnSearchText:
結局、はぐれちゃって……
ニナや監督たちも多分まだあの場所に……

engChrName: Oh, dear! We sh—hmm? Wait. You sound awfully familiar with—
engSearchText:
Oh, dear! We sh—hmm? Wait. You sound awfully
familiar with—
jpnChrName: グリムキャッツさん…… ………ニナ？　監督…………？
jpnSearchText:
グリムキャッツさん……
………ニナ？　監督…………？

engChrName: All right. Now it's my turn to start making demands!
engSearchText: All right. Now it's my turn to start making demands!
jpnChrName: ──というわけで、 今度はこっちが要求する番よ！
jpnSearchText:
──というわけで、
今度はこっちが要求する番よ！

engChrName: Access to the staircase is locked, and only this keycard can unlock it!
engSearchText:
Access to the staircase is locked, and only
this keycard can unlock it!
jpnChrName: 階段はロックがかかってる── 開けられるのはこのカードだけ！
jpnSearchText:
階段はロックがかかってる──
開けられるのはこのカードだけ！

engChrName: So if you want to progress any farther, you'll have to lend me a hand!
engSearchText:
So if you want to progress any farther, you'll have to
lend me a hand!
jpnChrName: 上に向かいたければ あたしに手を貸してもらうわ！
jpnSearchText:
上に向かいたければ
あたしに手を貸してもらうわ！

engChrName: Secured that card in advance, huh?
engSearchText: Secured that card in advance, huh?
jpnChrName: カードキー……成程、 “前もって”確保してやがったか。
jpnSearchText:
カードキー……成程、
“前もって”確保してやがったか。

engChrName: Really living up to your name as the burglar queen.
engSearchText: Really living up to your name as the burglar queen.
jpnChrName: ハッ、コソドロの面目躍如ってか？
jpnSearchText: ハッ、コソドロの面目躍如ってか？

engChrName: I am a PHANTOM THIEF, not a burglar! And my work is only just starting.
engSearchText:
I am a PHANTOM THIEF, not a burglar! And my
work is only just starting.
jpnChrName: 怪・盗！ フン、それに本命はこれからよ。
jpnSearchText:
怪・盗！
フン、それに本命はこれからよ。

engChrName: They might think they've stolen this festival and its participants from us, but I'm going to steal them right back!
engSearchText:
They might think they've stolen this festival and its
participants from us, but I'm going to steal them
right back!
jpnChrName: 連中に乗っ取られた映画祭を、 捕まってる皆を、何としても奪い返す……！
jpnSearchText:
連中に乗っ取られた映画祭を、
捕まってる皆を、何としても奪い返す……！

engChrName: But even I can't handle a job like this alone, so I'm gonna give you the honor of helping me!
engSearchText:
But even I can't handle a job like this alone, so I'm
gonna give you the honor of helping me!
jpnChrName: でも一人じゃちょっとだけ難しそうだから アンタたちに手伝わせてあげるってだけ！
jpnSearchText:
でも一人じゃちょっとだけ難しそうだから
アンタたちに手伝わせてあげるってだけ！

engChrName: You better not have any problems with that!
engSearchText: You better not have any problems with that!
jpnChrName: ──文句ある！？
jpnSearchText: ──文句ある！？

engChrName: No way! We'd really appreciate the help!
engSearchText: No way! We'd really appreciate the help!
jpnChrName: いえっ、願ってもないです！
jpnSearchText: いえっ、願ってもないです！

engChrName: The odds are very much stacked against us. We welcome any aid you have to offer.
engSearchText:
The odds are very much stacked against us.
We welcome any aid you have to offer.
jpnChrName: いまだ厳しい状況── 戦力的には渡りに船かと。
jpnSearchText:
いまだ厳しい状況──
戦力的には渡りに船かと。

engChrName: Even if it IS from Puss in Spandex. Beggars can't be choosers, I guess.
engSearchText:
Even if it IS from Puss in Spandex. Beggars can't be
choosers, I guess.
jpnChrName: それこそ猫の手もってヤツだ。 よろしく頼むぜ、怪盗さんよ。
jpnSearchText:
それこそ猫の手もってヤツだ。
よろしく頼むぜ、怪盗さんよ。

engChrName: Puss in WHAT?! Oh, whatever. It's a deal, then.
engSearchText: Puss in WHAT?! Oh, whatever. It's a deal, then.
jpnChrName: 猫の手言うな！　まあいいわ、 とにかく共同戦線成立ってわけね。
jpnSearchText:
猫の手言うな！　まあいいわ、
とにかく共同戦線成立ってわけね。

engChrName: Let's get moving. We need to make it to the top floor, where the awards were going to be presented!
engSearchText:
Let's get moving. We need to make it to the top
floor, where the awards were going to be presented!
jpnChrName: それじゃあ改めて目指すわよ、 ホテル最上階──受賞式会場をね！
jpnSearchText:
それじゃあ改めて目指すわよ、
ホテル最上階──受賞式会場をね！

engChrName: Right!
engSearchText: Right!
jpnChrName: 了解（ウーラ）っ！
jpnSearchText: 了解（ウーラ）っ！

engChrName: *sigh* Man, she's got the looks. It's just a shame about...everything else.
engSearchText:
*sigh* Man, she's got the looks. It's just a shame
about...everything else.
jpnChrName: ハア、しっかしイイ女なのに どこまでも残念っつーか……
jpnSearchText:
ハア、しっかしイイ女なのに
どこまでも残念っつーか……

engChrName: (Umm... No, I suppose it can wait until all of this is over.)
engSearchText:
(Umm... No, I suppose it can wait until all of this
is over.)
jpnChrName: （……えっと。   うん、今は後回しですよね……！）
jpnSearchText:
（……えっと。
うん、今は後回しですよね……！）

engChrName: Judi—...Ahem. 'Grimcat the Phantom Thief' joined the party as a guest.
engSearchText:
Judi—...Ahem. 'Grimcat the Phantom Thief'
joined the party as a guest.
jpnChrName: ジュディ──怪盗グリムキャッツが ゲストとして加入しました。
jpnSearchText:
ジュディ──怪盗グリムキャッツが
ゲストとして加入しました。
……！

engChrName: L-Look!
engSearchText: L-Look!
jpnChrName: あ、あれは……！
jpnSearchText: あ、あれは……！

engChrName: Wow...
engSearchText: Wow...
jpnSearchText: ………凄い…………

engChrName: They're both deeply captivating.
engSearchText: They're both deeply captivating.
jpnChrName: ……ええ、どちらも。
jpnSearchText: ……ええ、どちらも。

engChrName: Heh. Saara's holdin' her own pretty well.
engSearchText: Heh. Saara's holdin' her own pretty well.
jpnChrName: ハン── 何とか踏ん張ってるみてぇだな。
jpnSearchText:
ハン──
何とか踏ん張ってるみてぇだな。

engChrName: Oh, absolutely. It's quite an achievement to be able to keep up with one enhanced to superhuman levels by that mask. ♪
engSearchText:
Oh, absolutely. It's quite an achievement to be able to
keep up with one enhanced to superhuman levels by
that mask. ♪
jpnChrName: フフ、仮面で強化された“超人”相手に よく食らいつけるもんだよねぇ♪
jpnSearchText:
フフ、仮面で強化された“超人”相手に
よく食らいつけるもんだよねぇ♪

engChrName: It's because she's Shaheena's sister!
engSearchText: It's because she's Shaheena's sister!
jpnChrName: “お姉ちゃん”だからです！
jpnSearchText: “お姉ちゃん”だからです！

engChrName: Cue the psycho.
engSearchText: Cue the psycho.
jpnChrName: 出やがったなサイコ野郎……！
jpnSearchText: 出やがったなサイコ野郎……！

engChrName: Y-You came!
engSearchText: Y-You came!
jpnChrName: み、皆さん……！
jpnSearchText: み、皆さん……！

engChrName: Our saviors! Are we glad to see you!
engSearchText: Our saviors! Are we glad to see you!
jpnChrName: おおっ、助けに来てくれたんじゃな！？
jpnSearchText: おおっ、助けに来てくれたんじゃな！？

engChrName: Nina! Mr. Gotti!
engSearchText: Nina! Mr. Gotti!
jpnChrName: ニナさん、ゴッチ監督も……！
jpnSearchText: ニナさん、ゴッチ監督も……！

engChrName: It looks like neither of them are hurt, thank Aidios.
engSearchText: It looks like neither of them are hurt, thank Aidios.
jpnChrName: ……とりあえず 怪我とかはないみたいね。
jpnSearchText:
……とりあえず
怪我とかはないみたいね。

engChrName: G-Grimcat! What's that spicy cougar doing here?!
engSearchText: G-Grimcat! What's that spicy cougar doing here?!
jpnChrName: グ、グリムキャッツ……！？ 噂のけしからん雌猫がどうして！？
jpnSearchText:
グ、グリムキャッツ……！？
噂のけしからん雌猫がどうして！？

engChrName: I'm too young to be a COUGAR, thank you!
engSearchText: I'm too young to be a COUGAR, thank you!
jpnChrName: けしからん言うなっ！
jpnSearchText: けしからん言うなっ！

engChrName: What ARE you doing here, though?
engSearchText: What ARE you doing here, though?
jpnChrName: でも、どうしてここに……
jpnSearchText: でも、どうしてここに……

engChrName: Ahhhhh... Umm, well, I was asked by an actress to come and...help, you see!
engSearchText:
Ahhhhh... Umm, well, I was asked by an actress to
come and...help, you see!
jpnChrName: あー……まあちょっと とある女優に頼まれちゃってね。
jpnSearchText:
あー……まあちょっと
とある女優に頼まれちゃってね。

engChrName: So you're the phantom thief people are talking about... Come to steal our 'treasure,' I take it?
engSearchText:
So you're the phantom thief people are
talking about... Come to steal our 'treasure,' I take it?
jpnChrName: 巷で噂の怪盗だっけ── 僕らの“お宝”を奪いに来たのかな？
jpnSearchText:
巷で噂の怪盗だっけ──
僕らの“お宝”を奪いに来たのかな？

engChrName: I didn't realize you were working hand in hand—or rather, paw in hand—with the spriggan.
engSearchText:
I didn't realize you were working hand in hand—or
rather, paw in hand—with the spriggan.
jpnChrName: 裏解決屋（君たち）と対立してたかと思ったけど。
jpnSearchText: 裏解決屋（君たち）と対立してたかと思ったけど。

engChrName: We're not friends or anything... Just united in wanting to smash your face in.
engSearchText:
We're not friends or anything... Just united in
wanting to smash your face in.
jpnChrName: 別に仲良くはしちゃいねぇさ…… てめぇらをブチのめすのに都合がいいだけだ。
jpnSearchText:
別に仲良くはしちゃいねぇさ……
てめぇらをブチのめすのに都合がいいだけだ。

engChrName: Not just for what you did to Aida, but for all the hurt you caused Shaheena and so many others in Tharbad, too!
engSearchText:
Not just for what you did to Aida, but for all the hurt
you caused Shaheena and so many others in
Tharbad, too!
jpnChrName: ……はい、仇討ちだけじゃなく、 シャヒーナさんたちのためにも。
jpnSearchText:
……はい、仇討ちだけじゃなく、
シャヒーナさんたちのためにも。

engChrName: Could we perhaps tone the noise down?
engSearchText: Could we perhaps tone the noise down?
jpnChrName: ──悪いが、 少し静かにしてもらおうか。
jpnSearchText:
──悪いが、
少し静かにしてもらおうか。

engChrName: The show is almost at its climax.
engSearchText: The show is almost at its climax.
jpnChrName: 舞台もいよいよクライマックスに 差し掛かったところだ……
jpnSearchText:
舞台もいよいよクライマックスに
差し掛かったところだ……

engChrName: It would be a shame to miss it over a bout of petty sniping.
engSearchText:
It would be a shame to miss it over a bout of
petty sniping.
jpnChrName: ここで見逃したら勿体ないだろう？
jpnSearchText: ここで見逃したら勿体ないだろう？
っ……

engChrName: Haha. Sorry about that, boss. ❤
engSearchText: Haha. Sorry about that, boss. ❤
jpnChrName: フフ──ごめんよ、ボス❤
jpnSearchText: フフ──ごめんよ、ボス❤
……！

engChrName: Wait... Are you telling me...?
engSearchText: Wait... Are you telling me...?
jpnChrName: ……おい、まさか……
jpnSearchText: ……おい、まさか……

engChrName: N-No way...
engSearchText: N-No way...
jpnChrName: あ、あの人が……
jpnSearchText: あ、あの人が……

engChrName: My name is Gerard Dantès, the head of Almata.
engSearchText: My name is Gerard Dantès, the head of Almata.
jpnChrName: 《アルマータ》を仕切っている ジェラール・ダンテスという。
jpnSearchText:
《アルマータ》を仕切っている
ジェラール・ダンテスという。

engChrName: So you are the spriggan. Somehow this doesn't quite feel like our first encounter.
engSearchText:
So you are the spriggan. Somehow this doesn't quite
feel like our first encounter.
jpnChrName: 裏解決屋──だったか？ 初めましてという気はしないな。
jpnSearchText:
裏解決屋──だったか？
初めましてという気はしないな。

engChrName: Would you care to join us in watching the show? It seems, perhaps, that this was fated to be.
engSearchText:
Would you care to join us in watching the show?
It seems, perhaps, that this was fated to be.
jpnChrName: これまでの縁もある── 良ければ一緒に観ていくといい。
jpnSearchText:
これまでの縁もある──
良ければ一緒に観ていくといい。

engChrName: Heh. We plan to see this to the end...but hell if we're gonna do it with you.
engSearchText:
Heh. We plan to see this to the end...but hell if we're
gonna do it with you.
jpnChrName: ……ハッ、見届けはするが 一緒にっつーのは遠慮しておくぜ。
jpnSearchText:
……ハッ、見届けはするが
一緒にっつーのは遠慮しておくぜ。

engChrName: That'd just rain all over the hard work these kids've put in.
engSearchText:
That'd just rain all over the hard work these kids've
put in.
jpnChrName: あの子たちの頑張りに ケチが付いちまいそうだからな。
jpnSearchText:
あの子たちの頑張りに
ケチが付いちまいそうだからな。

engChrName: Hmm... A pity.
engSearchText: Hmm... A pity.
jpnChrName: フフ、それは残念だ。
jpnSearchText: フフ、それは残念だ。

engChrName: Almata's leader. An SS-level threat.
engSearchText: Almata's leader. An SS-level threat.
jpnChrName: 《アルマータ》の首領（ドン）── 脅威度ＳＳクラスの危険人物ですか。
jpnSearchText:
《アルマータ》の首領（ドン）──
脅威度ＳＳクラスの危険人物ですか。

engChrName: Fate notwithstanding, you are correct. This isn't even our first time meeting in this city.
engSearchText:
Fate notwithstanding, you are correct. This isn't even
our first time meeting in this city.
jpnChrName: これまでの縁はともかく──確かに この地でも初めてではありませんね？
jpnSearchText:
これまでの縁はともかく──確かに
この地でも初めてではありませんね？

engChrName: ...What?
engSearchText: ...What?
jpnSearchText: ……なに……

engChrName: *gasp* You don't mean...
engSearchText: *gasp* You don't mean...
jpnChrName: ……！ も、もしかして……
jpnSearchText:
……！
も、もしかして……

engChrName: He was that guy in the casino?!
engSearchText: He was that guy in the casino?!
jpnChrName: カジノにいた……
jpnSearchText: カジノにいた……

engChrName: There I was, thinkin' Almata had no presence here in this city...
engSearchText:
There I was, thinkin' Almata had no presence here in
this city...
jpnChrName: ……構成員や半グレの影はねぇ、 なんてのはとんだ見込み違いか。
jpnSearchText:
……構成員や半グレの影はねぇ、
なんてのはとんだ見込み違いか。

engChrName: ...when their leader was hidin' in plain sight the whole damn time.
engSearchText:
...when their leader was hidin' in plain sight the
whole damn time.
jpnChrName: まさかアタマ自らが 最初から潜伏してたとはな。
jpnSearchText:
まさかアタマ自らが
最初から潜伏してたとはな。

engChrName: It's simply a matter of efficiency. I believe in taking a hands-on approach to my work.
engSearchText:
It's simply a matter of efficiency. I believe in taking a
hands-on approach to my work.
jpnChrName: なに、効率の問題だ。 これでも“現場主義”なんでな。
jpnSearchText:
なに、効率の問題だ。
これでも“現場主義”なんでな。

engChrName: Whether it is disposing of pawns and abandoning positions, or giving tools and products a firsthand trial.
engSearchText:
Whether it is disposing of pawns and abandoning
positions, or giving tools and products a
firsthand trial.
jpnChrName: 用済みの駒と陣地の廃棄に、 “鍵”と“商品”の試験運用も含めて。
jpnSearchText:
用済みの駒と陣地の廃棄に、
“鍵”と“商品”の試験運用も含めて。

engChrName: You son of a bitch...
engSearchText: You son of a bitch...
jpnSearchText: ……てめえ………

engChrName: Now I get it.
engSearchText: Now I get it.
jpnChrName: ……なるほどな。
jpnSearchText: ……なるほどな。

engChrName: There's a lot goin' on here, but your main goal here was some kinda experiment.
engSearchText:
There's a lot goin' on here, but your main goal here
was some kinda experiment.
jpnChrName: 色々ありそうだがお前らの主目的は 要するに“実験”だったってワケか。
jpnSearchText:
色々ありそうだがお前らの主目的は
要するに“実験”だったってワケか。

engChrName: To see just what you could pull off by combining those drugs with that device.
engSearchText:
To see just what you could pull off by combining
those drugs with that device.
jpnChrName: その装置と、ドラッグを組み合わせて どれだけのことを引き起こせるかの。
jpnSearchText:
その装置と、ドラッグを組み合わせて
どれだけのことを引き起こせるかの。

engChrName: Wha...?
engSearchText: Wha...?
jpnSearchText: あ……

engChrName: That does fit with what they were trying to do in Creil and Langport, too.
engSearchText:
That does fit with what they were trying to do in
Creil and Langport, too.
jpnChrName: クレイユやラングポートでも そんなことを言ってましたが……
jpnSearchText:
クレイユやラングポートでも
そんなことを言ってましたが……

engChrName: So this chaos right now isn't a means to an end, it's an end in itself?
engSearchText:
So this chaos right now isn't a means to an end, it's
an end in itself?
jpnChrName: 今のこの状況──“手段”ではなく、 そのものが“目的”だったんですね？
jpnSearchText:
今のこの状況──“手段”ではなく、
そのものが“目的”だったんですね？

engChrName: Correct.
engSearchText: Correct.
jpnChrName: フフ……正解だ。
jpnSearchText: フフ……正解だ。

engChrName: Whether it was securing new distribution routes, or testing our ability to use this heirloom to instigate an uprising of sorts...
engSearchText:
Whether it was securing new distribution routes, or
testing our ability to use this heirloom to instigate an
uprising of sorts...
jpnChrName: “嗜好品”を絡めた新たな流通ルートに “遺産”を介した人工的な暴動発生。
jpnSearchText:
“嗜好品”を絡めた新たな流通ルートに
“遺産”を介した人工的な暴動発生。

engChrName: ...the data we've obtained from this promises to be quite valuable in what is to come.
engSearchText:
...the data we've obtained from this promises to be
quite valuable in what is to come.
jpnChrName: どのデータも今後の展開に それなりに有意義ではあるだろう。
jpnSearchText:
どのデータも今後の展開に
それなりに有意義ではあるだろう。

engChrName: The mask cannot be reused, alas—but I believe this to be a satisfactory application.
engSearchText:
The mask cannot be reused, alas—but I believe this to
be a satisfactory application.
jpnChrName: あの“仮面”は一回限りだが ああいう使い方ならば惜しくはない。
jpnSearchText:
あの“仮面”は一回限りだが
ああいう使い方ならば惜しくはない。

engChrName: Good work, Melchior.
engSearchText: Good work, Melchior.
jpnChrName: よくやったな──メルキオル。
jpnSearchText: よくやったな──メルキオル。

engChrName: Thanks, boss. ❤
engSearchText: Thanks, boss. ❤
jpnChrName: ありがと、ボス❤
jpnSearchText: ありがと、ボス❤

engChrName: That pretty thing latches on to the darkness and vulnerability in people's hearts, making puppets out of them.
engSearchText:
That pretty thing latches on to the darkness and
vulnerability in people's hearts, making puppets out
of them.
jpnChrName: 人の弱みや昏い部分に取り憑いて “力”の代行者として傀儡化する──
jpnSearchText:
人の弱みや昏い部分に取り憑いて
“力”の代行者として傀儡化する──

engChrName: I'm glad I was able to steal a spare during the chaos in Crossbell a year and a half ago. ♪
engSearchText:
I'm glad I was able to steal a spare during the chaos in
Crossbell a year and a half ago. ♪
jpnChrName: 一年半前にクロスベルに探りを入れて “予備”を盗んだ甲斐があったよ♪
jpnSearchText:
一年半前にクロスベルに探りを入れて
“予備”を盗んだ甲斐があったよ♪

engChrName: They're...total monsters...
engSearchText: They're...total monsters...
jpnChrName: ……なんて人たち………
jpnSearchText: ……なんて人たち………

engChrName: Yes. We may need to increase their threat level to SS+.
engSearchText:
Yes. We may need to increase their threat level
to SS+.
jpnChrName: ……脅威度ＳＳ＋に 格上げが必要そうですね……
jpnSearchText:
……脅威度ＳＳ＋に
格上げが必要そうですね……

engChrName: (Huh... That was one of the many crises SHE was involved in...)
engSearchText:
(Huh... That was one of the many crises
SHE was involved in...)
jpnChrName: （そうか──   “彼女”が関わったっていう。）
jpnSearchText:
（そうか──
“彼女”が関わったっていう。）

engChrName: We will not allow this madness to go on a moment longer!
engSearchText:
We will not allow this madness to go on
a moment longer!
jpnChrName: ……これ以上こんな事を 続けさせるわけにはいきません。
jpnSearchText:
……これ以上こんな事を
続けさせるわけにはいきません。

engChrName: We're taking that Genesis back from you, whatever it takes!
engSearchText:
We're taking that Genesis back from you, whatever
it takes!
jpnChrName: その《ゲネシス》── 何としても手放してもらいます……！
jpnSearchText:
その《ゲネシス》──
何としても手放してもらいます……！

engChrName: Oh! Well, you can have it.
engSearchText: Oh! Well, you can have it.
jpnChrName: ああ、別にそれは構わんぞ？
jpnSearchText: ああ、別にそれは構わんぞ？

engChrName: These devices were designed to eventually come into the hands of their rightful owners regardless. That is their nature.
engSearchText:
These devices were designed to eventually come into
the hands of their rightful owners regardless. That is
their nature.
jpnChrName: いずれ正当な所有者の元に集まる── 元々そういう代物のようだからな。
jpnSearchText:
いずれ正当な所有者の元に集まる──
元々そういう代物のようだからな。

engChrName: What...?
engSearchText: What...?
jpnSearchText: え───

engChrName: Sounds like you have a lot of info you could share with us.
engSearchText:
Sounds like you have a lot of info you could share
with us.
jpnChrName: ……どうやら 色々ご存じのようじゃねえか？
jpnSearchText:
……どうやら
色々ご存じのようじゃねえか？

engChrName: Perhaps. Yet only a fraction of all there is to know.
engSearchText: Perhaps. Yet only a fraction of all there is to know.
jpnChrName: フフ、ほんの一部ではあるがな。
jpnSearchText: フフ、ほんの一部ではあるがな。

engChrName: Now that we have seen the fruits of our labor, our work here is done.
engSearchText:
Now that we have seen the fruits of our labor, our
work here is done.
jpnChrName: ──さて、こちらとしては成果を 確認できた時点で目的は達成している。
jpnSearchText:
──さて、こちらとしては成果を
確認できた時点で目的は達成している。

engChrName: Withdrawing would be a valid option. However...
engSearchText: Withdrawing would be a valid option. However...
jpnChrName: このまま退いてもいいんだが……
jpnSearchText: このまま退いてもいいんだが……

engChrName: Wha...?
engSearchText: Wha...?
jpnSearchText: なっ……！？

engChrName: Prince Sherid...?
engSearchText: Prince Sherid...?
jpnChrName: シェ、シェリド殿下……？
jpnSearchText: シェ、シェリド殿下……？

engChrName: And Naje, too... I thought the two of you had escaped?
engSearchText:
And Naje, too... I thought the two of you
had escaped?
jpnChrName: ナージェ嬢も── 何とか逃れたんじゃあ……！？
jpnSearchText:
ナージェ嬢も──
何とか逃れたんじゃあ……！？
っ………！

engChrName: ...I'm sorry, everyone.
engSearchText: ...I'm sorry, everyone.
jpnChrName: ……ヴァン君たち………すまない。
jpnSearchText: ……ヴァン君たち………すまない。

engChrName: Don't tell me...
engSearchText: Don't tell me...
jpnChrName: ！　まさか……！
jpnSearchText: ！　まさか……！

engChrName: You've had some of that drug, too?!
engSearchText: You've had some of that drug, too?!
jpnChrName: 殿下たちにも あの薬物の成分を……！？
jpnSearchText:
殿下たちにも
あの薬物の成分を……！？

engChrName: Ahaha! Yep! All it took was a few little droplets in their welcome drink. ❤
engSearchText:
Ahaha! Yep! All it took was a few little droplets in
their welcome drink. ❤
jpnChrName: あはは、正解！ ウェルカムドリンクにほんの数滴ね❤
jpnSearchText:
あはは、正解！
ウェルカムドリンクにほんの数滴ね❤

engChrName: Here is the final amusement of the festival.
engSearchText: Here is the final amusement of the festival.
jpnChrName: これが最後の余興だ。
jpnSearchText: これが最後の余興だ。

engChrName: I do hope you can keep me at least as entertained as those dancers did.
engSearchText:
I do hope you can keep me at least as entertained as
those dancers did.
jpnChrName: あの踊り手たちに負けないくらい 存分に愉しませてもらおうか？
jpnSearchText:
あの踊り手たちに負けないくらい
存分に愉しませてもらおうか？

engChrName: Ngh... Aaaaaargh!
engSearchText: Ngh... Aaaaaargh!
jpnChrName: っ……おおおおおおっ……！！
jpnSearchText: っ……おおおおおおっ……！！

engChrName: Nnrrgh...!
engSearchText: Nnrrgh...!
jpnChrName: ぐううううううっ……！！
jpnSearchText: ぐううううううっ……！！

engChrName: Catgirls and gentlemen!
engSearchText: Catgirls and gentlemen!
jpnChrName: さぁさ、お立ち会い──
jpnSearchText: さぁさ、お立ち会い──

engChrName: In one corner, we have none other than a crown prince of the desert and his ever-so loyal servant!
engSearchText:
In one corner, we have none other than a crown
prince of the desert and his ever-so loyal servant!
jpnChrName: 目くるめく祭りのトリを飾るのは、 熱砂の国の公太子とその忠実なる僕（しもべ）。
jpnSearchText:
目くるめく祭りのトリを飾るのは、
熱砂の国の公太子とその忠実なる僕（しもべ）。

engChrName: And in the other, we have the simple spriggan of Edith. Just who between them will emerge victorious?
engSearchText:
And in the other, we have the simple spriggan
of Edith. Just who between them will
emerge victorious?
jpnChrName: 挑みたるは首都の裏解決屋── 果たしてその運命やいかに♪
jpnSearchText:
挑みたるは首都の裏解決屋──
果たしてその運命やいかに♪

engChrName: Those golden auras are bad news...
engSearchText: Those golden auras are bad news...
jpnChrName: お、黄金の闘気……
jpnSearchText: お、黄金の闘気……

engChrName: We're really in it now!
engSearchText: We're really in it now!
jpnChrName: ヤベえな、こりゃ……！
jpnSearchText: ヤベえな、こりゃ……！

engChrName: This tension... It's incomparable to that of our fight in the cave!
engSearchText:
This tension... It's incomparable to that of our fight
in the cave!
jpnChrName: 霊圧上昇──砂岩窟の時とは 比較にならないでしょう！
jpnSearchText:
霊圧上昇──砂岩窟の時とは
比較にならないでしょう！

engChrName: Take care!
engSearchText: Take care!
jpnChrName: み、皆さん……！
jpnSearchText: み、皆さん……！

engChrName: Wh-What are you gonna do?!
engSearchText: Wh-What are you gonna do?!
jpnChrName: ど、どうするつもりじゃあ！？
jpnSearchText: ど、どうするつもりじゃあ！？

engChrName: We're gonna neutralize 'em—we ain't got any other options!
engSearchText:
We're gonna neutralize 'em—we ain't got
any other options!
jpnChrName: こうなりゃ是非もねぇ…… まずは無力化させてもらいますよ！
jpnSearchText:
こうなりゃ是非もねぇ……
まずは無力化させてもらいますよ！

engChrName: They're sponsors to the festival! We need to make them see sense!
engSearchText:
They're sponsors to the festival! We need to make
them see sense!
jpnChrName: 大切なスポンサーだからこそ 何とか目覚めさせてみせるわっ！
jpnSearchText:
大切なスポンサーだからこそ
何とか目覚めさせてみせるわっ！

engChrName: Right! Saara and Shaheena are depending on us, too!
engSearchText: Right! Saara and Shaheena are depending on us, too!
jpnChrName: はい……！　サァラさんや シャヒーナさんたちのためにも……！
jpnSearchText:
はい……！　サァラさんや
シャヒーナさんたちのためにも……！

engChrName: ...Well fought.
engSearchText: ...Well fought.
jpnChrName: っ……お見事です……
jpnSearchText: っ……お見事です……

engChrName: Haha. That it was.
engSearchText: Haha. That it was.
jpnChrName: ……ハハ、さすがだな……
jpnSearchText: ……ハハ、さすがだな……

engChrName: They're back to normal!
engSearchText: They're back to normal!
jpnChrName: お二人が元に……！
jpnSearchText: お二人が元に……！

engChrName: W-We did it!
engSearchText: W-We did it!
jpnChrName: や、やりましたね……！
jpnSearchText: や、やりましたね……！

engChrName: On the contrary. We've hardly started.
engSearchText: On the contrary. We've hardly started.
jpnChrName: ──いや、ここからだ。
jpnSearchText: ──いや、ここからだ。

engChrName: This device can do far, far more.
engSearchText: This device can do far, far more.
jpnChrName: コイツにはまだ“先”がある。
jpnSearchText: コイツにはまだ“先”がある。

engChrName: For it is capable of stimulating the emotion that lies at the root of all others: fear.
engSearchText:
For it is capable of stimulating the emotion that lies
at the root of all others: fear.
jpnChrName: あらゆる感情の根源にあるもの…… “恐怖”を揺り動かすほどの機（はたらき）が。
jpnSearchText:
あらゆる感情の根源にあるもの……
“恐怖”を揺り動かすほどの機（はたらき）が。

engChrName: Now, why don't you show me yours?
engSearchText: Now, why don't you show me yours?
jpnChrName: さあ──見せてもらおうか！？
jpnSearchText: さあ──見せてもらおうか！？

engChrName: Ugh... AAAAAAAAAAAAGH!
engSearchText: Ugh... AAAAAAAAAAAAGH!
jpnChrName: ッ、ああああああああああっ……！？
jpnSearchText: ッ、ああああああああああっ……！？

engChrName: Naje!
engSearchText: Naje!
jpnChrName: ナージェ……！？
jpnSearchText: ナージェ……！？

engChrName: Urgh... My... My mana is—?!
engSearchText: Urgh... My... My mana is—?!
jpnChrName: ……ぐうっ…… これは、私の霊力（マナ）を……！？
jpnSearchText:
……ぐうっ……
これは、私の霊力（マナ）を……！？

engChrName: You gotta be shittin' me...
engSearchText: You gotta be shittin' me...
jpnChrName: ！？　まさか──
jpnSearchText: ！？　まさか──

engChrName: It's like what I went through!
engSearchText: It's like what I went through!
jpnChrName: 俺の時と同じ……！？
jpnSearchText: 俺の時と同じ……！？

engChrName: AAAAAAAAARGH!
engSearchText: AAAAAAAAARGH!
jpnChrName: オオオオオオオオオオオオンンッ！！！
jpnSearchText: オオオオオオオオオオオオンンッ！！！

engChrName: What in the...?!
engSearchText: What in the...?!
jpnChrName: ウ、ウソでしょ……！？
jpnSearchText: ウ、ウソでしょ……！？

engChrName: I-It really is what happened to Aida and Aaron...
engSearchText: I-It really is what happened to Aida and Aaron...
jpnChrName: ア、アイーダさんや アーロンさんの時みたいな……！
jpnSearchText:
ア、アイーダさんや
アーロンさんの時みたいな……！

engChrName: The legendary Verethragna...
engSearchText: The legendary Verethragna...
jpnChrName: ……お伽話の、雷獣王（ウルスラグナ）……
jpnSearchText: ……お伽話の、雷獣王（ウルスラグナ）……

engChrName: Ahaha! A being from a higher plane? Looks like you managed to reel in a big one, boss!
engSearchText:
Ahaha! A being from a higher plane? Looks like you
managed to reel in a big one, boss!
jpnChrName: アハハ、どうやら高位次元の ヤバいのを引き込んじゃったみたいだね！
jpnSearchText:
アハハ、どうやら高位次元の
ヤバいのを引き込んじゃったみたいだね！

engChrName: Everyone... You need to run...
engSearchText: Everyone... You need to run...
jpnChrName: ……君たち……逃げたま──
jpnSearchText: ……君たち……逃げたま──

engChrName: ROOOOOOOOOAR!
engSearchText: ROOOOOOOOOAR!
jpnChrName: ガアアアアアアアッ……！！
jpnSearchText: ガアアアアアアアッ……！！

engChrName: Nngh! / Aaaaaah!
engSearchText: Nngh! / Aaaaaah!
engHtmlText: リゼット＆グリムキャッツ
jpnChrName: っ……！！／きゃああっ！？
jpnSearchText: っ……！！／きゃああっ！？

engChrName: Argh!
engSearchText: Argh!
jpnChrName: ああっ……！
jpnSearchText: ああっ……！

engChrName: Whoaaa!
engSearchText: Whoaaa!
jpnChrName: のわあああああっ……！？
jpnSearchText: のわあああああっ……！？

！　凄く消耗してるみたい……
大丈夫ですか！？

engChrName: *huff* I'm fine... *huff* Really. I've just been running around this whole time, that's all.
engSearchText:
*huff* I'm fine... *huff* Really. I've just been running
around this whole time, that's all.
jpnChrName: ぜえはあ、平気よ平気…… ずっと逃げ回ってただけだから……
jpnSearchText:
ぜえはあ、平気よ平気……
ずっと逃げ回ってただけだから……

engChrName: Judith, did you see her? Grimcat was here in the flesh, baby!
engSearchText:
Judith, did you see her? Grimcat was here in the
flesh, baby!
jpnChrName: ジュディス君、見たかねっ！？ あの“生グリムキャッツ”をっ……！
jpnSearchText:
ジュディス君、見たかねっ！？
あの“生グリムキャッツ”をっ……！

engChrName: If she's not a scintillating spectacle, I don't know who is! That woman is the living embodiment of one of my 108 ideal forms!
engSearchText:
If she's not a scintillating spectacle, I don't know
who is! That woman is the living embodiment of one
of my 108 ideal forms!
jpnChrName: あれぞまさにセクシー＆スペクタクル！！ ワシの１０８ある理想形の一つと言えようっ！
jpnSearchText:
あれぞまさにセクシー＆スペクタクル！！
ワシの１０８ある理想形の一つと言えようっ！

engChrName: Aaargh, I've got to do something! I need to get to work on my next movie—one that'll put that damn Lam in his place!
engSearchText:
Aaargh, I've got to do something! I need to get to
work on my next movie—one that'll put that damn
Lam in his place!
jpnChrName: ぬおおおっ、こうしちゃおれんっ！ ラムのヤツに勝つための作品作りをっ……！
jpnSearchText:
ぬおおおっ、こうしちゃおれんっ！
ラムのヤツに勝つための作品作りをっ……！

engChrName: Ahaha. Already have your eyes on the next prize, Mr. Gotti?
engSearchText:
Ahaha. Already have your eyes on the next prize,
Mr. Gotti?
jpnChrName: あはは…… さすがはゴッチ監督……
jpnSearchText:
あはは……
さすがはゴッチ監督……

engChrName: Eh, we could all learn a little from his determination. Though maybe not the part that's waist-deep in the gutters...
engSearchText:
Eh, we could all learn a little from his determination.
Though maybe not the part that's waist-deep in
the gutters...
jpnChrName: ま、まあ煩悩の数はさておき 負けん気は見習いたいかもね……
jpnSearchText:
ま、まあ煩悩の数はさておき
負けん気は見習いたいかもね……

engChrName: (We recovered another Genesis...but at what cost?)
engSearchText: (We recovered another Genesis...but at what cost?)
jpnChrName: （……今回もとんでもない事に……）
jpnSearchText: （……今回もとんでもない事に……）

engChrName: (Great-grandfather, Mom, Grandmother...)
engSearchText: (Great-grandfather, Mom, Grandmother...)
jpnChrName: （曾お祖父ちゃん……   ……お母さんにお祖母ちゃんも……）
jpnSearchText:
（曾お祖父ちゃん……
……お母さんにお祖母ちゃんも……）

engChrName: Well, I'd say this whole mess has given us a lot of food for thought.
engSearchText:
Well, I'd say this whole mess has given us a lot of
food for thought.
jpnChrName: ま、それぞれ思う所はあんだろう。
jpnSearchText: ま、それぞれ思う所はあんだろう。

engChrName: But our clients are safe and sound—well, mostly— and I don't think we could've wrapped things up much better than we did.
engSearchText:
But our clients are safe and sound—well, mostly—
and I don't think we could've wrapped things up
much better than we did.
jpnChrName: だが依頼人も全員無事──かは微妙だが、 何とか“落とし所”には持って行けた。
jpnSearchText:
だが依頼人も全員無事──かは微妙だが、
何とか“落とし所”には持って行けた。

engChrName: I can see us getting a juicy bonus for our work, too. So good job, guys—you all get a passin' grade.
engSearchText:
I can see us getting a juicy bonus for our work, too.
So good job, guys—you all get a passin' grade.
jpnChrName: 臨時ボーナスも入りそうだし、 良くやった──全員及第点をやるよ。
jpnSearchText:
臨時ボーナスも入りそうだし、
良くやった──全員及第点をやるよ。
あ……

engChrName: Aww... Heehee.
engSearchText: Aww... Heehee.
jpnSearchText: ……えへへ………

engChrName: I'm not sure where you get off thinking you, of all people, can grade us.
engSearchText:
I'm not sure where you get off thinking you, of all
people, can grade us.
jpnChrName: ヘッ……てめぇごときに 採点しきれる器じゃねえっつの。
jpnSearchText:
ヘッ……てめぇごときに
採点しきれる器じゃねえっつの。

engChrName: I suppose that now all of this is over, this concludes my current assignment.
engSearchText:
I suppose that now all of this is over, this concludes
my current assignment.
jpnChrName: ……ふふ、これにて 今回の“出向”も終わりですね。
jpnSearchText:
……ふふ、これにて
今回の“出向”も終わりですね。

engChrName: A job well done, Mr. Arkride. Everyone.
engSearchText: A job well done, Mr. Arkride. Everyone.
jpnChrName: お疲れ様でした── ヴァン様、皆様がたも。
jpnSearchText:
お疲れ様でした──
ヴァン様、皆様がたも。

engChrName: Right back at you, Risette.
engSearchText: Right back at you, Risette.
jpnChrName: ああ……つうかお前さんもな。
jpnSearchText: ああ……つうかお前さんもな。

engChrName: I really don't know what we would have done without you.
engSearchText:
I really don't know what we would have done
without you.
jpnChrName: ──リゼットさん、 本当にありがとうございました。
jpnSearchText:
──リゼットさん、
本当にありがとうございました。

engChrName: You've been so attentive and supportive—not to mention the way you saved Van when he was in danger.
engSearchText:
You've been so attentive and supportive—not to
mention the way you saved Van when he was
in danger.
jpnChrName: 細やかな気遣いにサポート…… ヴァンさんの危機も救ってくれましたし。
jpnSearchText:
細やかな気遣いにサポート……
ヴァンさんの危機も救ってくれましたし。

engChrName: Yeah! You've been super helpful to have around!
engSearchText: Yeah! You've been super helpful to have around!
jpnChrName: すっごく心強かったですっ！
jpnSearchText: すっごく心強かったですっ！

engChrName: You ever think about trading places with our boss? Work'd go way smoother with you running the show.
engSearchText:
You ever think about trading places with our boss?
Work'd go way smoother with you running the show.
jpnChrName: つうかマジで所長と入れ替えた方が 上手く回るんじゃねーか？
jpnSearchText:
つうかマジで所長と入れ替えた方が
上手く回るんじゃねーか？

engChrName: I'm RIGHT here! Though I'd, uh, be lying if I said I hadn't had the same thought.
engSearchText:
I'm RIGHT here! Though I'd, uh, be lying if I said I
hadn't had the same thought.
jpnChrName: ──ってオイ！ まあ俺もそう思わんでもねぇが……
jpnSearchText:
──ってオイ！
まあ俺もそう思わんでもねぇが……

engChrName: It was my pleasure. I had a wonderful time working with all of you.
engSearchText:
It was my pleasure. I had a wonderful time working
with all of you.
jpnChrName: こちらこそ── 良い経験をさせて頂きました。
jpnSearchText:
こちらこそ──
良い経験をさせて頂きました。

engChrName: Stay away! We won't try and fight you—just please don't come any closer!
engSearchText:
Stay away! We won't try and fight you—just please
don't come any closer!
jpnChrName: 抵抗はしないから これ以上は近づかないでくれ！
jpnSearchText:
抵抗はしないから
これ以上は近づかないでくれ！

engChrName: Only the finest level of service for our guests...
engSearchText: Only the finest level of service for our guests...
jpnChrName: お客様ニハ最上級ノゴ奉仕ヲ……
jpnSearchText: お客様ニハ最上級ノゴ奉仕ヲ……

engChrName: I-It's no use! We can't get through to them!
engSearchText: I-It's no use! We can't get through to them!
jpnChrName: だ、駄目です！　話が通じません！
jpnSearchText: だ、駄目です！　話が通じません！

engChrName: Someone, help!
engSearchText: Someone, help!

engChrName: Stop right there!
engSearchText: Stop right there!
jpnChrName: おっと、そこまでだ！
jpnSearchText: おっと、そこまでだ！

engChrName: We won't let you lay a finger on them!
engSearchText: We won't let you lay a finger on them!
jpnChrName: これ以上はさせません！
jpnSearchText: これ以上はさせません！

engChrName: Wh-Who are—?!
engSearchText: Wh-Who are—?!
jpnChrName: き、君たちは……！？
jpnSearchText: き、君たちは……！？

engChrName: You're the prize recipients, I assume? Please leave this to us!
engSearchText:
You're the prize recipients, I assume? Please leave this
to us!
jpnChrName: 監督に受賞者の方々ですね？ 後は私たちに任せてください！
jpnSearchText:
監督に受賞者の方々ですね？
後は私たちに任せてください！

engChrName: This ain't gonna be a fight scene in a movie! Stay back if you don't wanna get hurt!
engSearchText:
This ain't gonna be a fight scene in a movie!
Stay back if you don't wanna get hurt!
jpnChrName: ここからは殺陣じゃなく本物の戦闘だ、 怪我したくなけりゃ後ろに下がってな！
jpnSearchText:
ここからは殺陣じゃなく本物の戦闘だ、
怪我したくなけりゃ後ろに下がってな！

engChrName: Is everyone unharmed?
engSearchText: Is everyone unharmed?
jpnChrName: 皆さま、ご無事ですか？
jpnSearchText: 皆さま、ご無事ですか？

engChrName: Y-Yes, we're fine. Thank you.
engSearchText: Y-Yes, we're fine. Thank you.
jpnChrName: え、ええ……助かったわ。
jpnSearchText: え、ええ……助かったわ。

engChrName: We are in your debt. But just who are you?
engSearchText: We are in your debt. But just who are you?
jpnChrName: 恩に着るよ、しかし君たちは……
jpnSearchText: 恩に着るよ、しかし君たちは……

engChrName: That's gonna have to wait, I'm afraid.
engSearchText: That's gonna have to wait, I'm afraid.
jpnChrName: 時間があったら受賞作の話とかを じっくり聞かせてもらいたい所だが……
jpnSearchText:
時間があったら受賞作の話とかを
じっくり聞かせてもらいたい所だが……

engChrName: I'd love to hear all about your award winner, too, but we ain't got the time.
engSearchText:
I'd love to hear all about your award winner, too, but
we ain't got the time.
jpnChrName: 残念ながら今は急いでいてね。 細かいことは気にしないでくれや。
jpnSearchText:
残念ながら今は急いでいてね。
細かいことは気にしないでくれや。

engChrName: Y-Yes, I suppose you're right.
engSearchText: Y-Yes, I suppose you're right.
jpnChrName: あ、ああ……そうだったな。
jpnSearchText: あ、ああ……そうだったな。

engChrName: But I can tell you're strong, so I do have one favor I'd like to ask.
engSearchText:
But I can tell you're strong, so I do have one favor I'd
like to ask.
jpnChrName: では君たちの腕を見込んで 一つ頼みがある。
jpnSearchText:
では君たちの腕を見込んで
一つ頼みがある。

engChrName: Help Judith. Please.
engSearchText: Help Judith. Please.
jpnChrName: どうかジュディス君のことを 助けてあげてくれないか。
jpnSearchText:
どうかジュディス君のことを
助けてあげてくれないか。

engChrName: Judith? What happened to her?
engSearchText: Judith? What happened to her?
jpnChrName: ジュディスさん、ですか？
jpnSearchText: ジュディスさん、ですか？

engChrName: She volunteered to act as a decoy when we were still upstairs, to help us escape.
engSearchText:
She volunteered to act as a decoy when we were still
upstairs, to help us escape.
jpnChrName: ああ、彼女は私たちを逃がすため 上の階で囮になったんだ。
jpnSearchText:
ああ、彼女は私たちを逃がすため
上の階で囮になったんだ。

engChrName: Gotti and Nina weren't able to get away, but she bought the rest of us the chance to flee.
engSearchText:
Gotti and Nina weren't able to get away, but she
bought the rest of us the chance to flee.
jpnChrName: ゴッチ監督やニナ君も 取り残されてしまっていてね……
jpnSearchText:
ゴッチ監督やニナ君も
取り残されてしまっていてね……

engChrName: Oh, no...!
engSearchText: Oh, no...!
jpnChrName: そんな……！
jpnSearchText: そんな……！

engChrName: Got'cha. Consider it done.
engSearchText: Got'cha. Consider it done.
jpnChrName: そっちの事は任された。
jpnSearchText: そっちの事は任された。

engChrName: You guys just hole up somewhere safe until this is all over.
engSearchText:
You guys just hole up somewhere safe until this is
all over.
jpnChrName: 事態が収まるまで、アンタらは 安全な場所に立てこもってるといい。
jpnSearchText:
事態が収まるまで、アンタらは
安全な場所に立てこもってるといい。

engChrName: A-All right... We'll try.
engSearchText: A-All right... We'll try.
jpnChrName: わ、わかった……そうさせてもらうよ。
jpnSearchText: わ、わかった……そうさせてもらうよ。

engChrName: Please, save Judith and the others!
engSearchText: Please, save Judith and the others!
jpnChrName: ジュディスさんたちのことを お願いします……！
jpnSearchText:
ジュディスさんたちのことを
お願いします……！

engChrName: The team escorted the director, along with the actors and actresses, to a safe place.
engSearchText:
The team escorted the director, along with the actors
and actresses, to a safe place.
jpnChrName: ヴァン達は受賞者たちが 安全な場所に避難するのを見届けた。
jpnSearchText:
ヴァン達は受賞者たちが
安全な場所に避難するのを見届けた。

engChrName: I hope Judith and the others are all right...
engSearchText: I hope Judith and the others are all right...
jpnChrName: ジュディスさん、大丈夫でしょうか…… ニナさんにゴッチ監督も……
jpnSearchText:
ジュディスさん、大丈夫でしょうか……
ニナさんにゴッチ監督も……

engChrName: I dunno about the others, but I have a feeling Judith's fine.
engSearchText:
I dunno about the others, but I have a feeling
Judith's fine.
jpnChrName: まあ、ジュディスに関しては そこまで心配は要らないと思うが。
jpnSearchText:
まあ、ジュディスに関しては
そこまで心配は要らないと思うが。

engChrName: Me, too.
engSearchText: Me, too.
jpnChrName: はい、きっと。
jpnSearchText: はい、きっと。

engChrName: Yeah. She's in danger of a different sort, I bet.
engSearchText: Yeah. She's in danger of a different sort, I bet.
jpnChrName: まあ、あの痴女だしなぁ。
jpnSearchText: まあ、あの痴女だしなぁ。

engChrName: ...Hmm? What do you mean?
engSearchText: ...Hmm? What do you mean?
jpnChrName: ？　ええと、どうしてそんなことが……
jpnSearchText: ？　ええと、どうしてそんなことが……

engChrName: Regardless, we should hurry. Our objective hasn't changed.
engSearchText:
Regardless, we should hurry. Our objective
hasn't changed.
jpnChrName: ……とにかく今は先を急ぎましょう。 やるべき事は変わらないかと。
jpnSearchText:
……とにかく今は先を急ぎましょう。
やるべき事は変わらないかと。

engChrName: Yeah, you're right. Let's move.
engSearchText: Yeah, you're right. Let's move.
jpnChrName: だな──行くぞ。
jpnSearchText: だな──行くぞ。

engChrName: Well, look who it is.
engSearchText: Well, look who it is.
jpnChrName: あいつらは……！
jpnSearchText: あいつらは……！

engChrName: Almata's goons!
engSearchText: Almata's goons!
jpnChrName: アルマータの構成員か！
jpnSearchText: アルマータの構成員か！

engChrName: Who are you?!
engSearchText: Who are you?!
jpnChrName: 貴様らは……！？
jpnSearchText: 貴様らは……！？

engChrName: They must be the intruders we were warned about!
engSearchText: They must be the intruders we were warned about!
jpnChrName: 報告にあった侵入者か！
jpnSearchText: 報告にあった侵入者か！

engChrName: If you wanna avoid a world of pain, outta our way!
engSearchText: If you wanna avoid a world of pain, outta our way!
jpnChrName: 痛い目に遭いたくなかったら そこを退きなさい──！
jpnSearchText:
痛い目に遭いたくなかったら
そこを退きなさい──！

engChrName: I rather doubt they are open to discussion!
engSearchText: I rather doubt they are open to discussion!
jpnChrName: 彼らに言葉は無用でしょう！
jpnSearchText: 彼らに言葉は無用でしょう！

engChrName: Yeah. Don't hold back against 'em, just take 'em down!
engSearchText:
Yeah. Don't hold back against 'em, just take
'em down!
jpnChrName: 遠慮する必要は微塵もねえ、 強行突破するぞ！
jpnSearchText:
遠慮する必要は微塵もねえ、
強行突破するぞ！

engChrName: Right!
engSearchText: Right!
jpnChrName: はい……！
jpnSearchText: はい……！

engChrName: Got it!
engSearchText: Got it!
jpnChrName: 撃破しますっ！！
jpnSearchText: 撃破しますっ！！

engChrName: Hah! Don't say I didn't warn you!
engSearchText: Hah! Don't say I didn't warn you!
jpnChrName: フッ、ざまあみなさい！
jpnSearchText: フッ、ざまあみなさい！

engChrName: That was amazing...
engSearchText: That was amazing...
jpnChrName: やっぱりすごい身のこなし……
jpnSearchText: やっぱりすごい身のこなし……

engChrName: Looked like you were doing wire stunts. You pull those moves out while you're filming, too?
engSearchText:
Looked like you were doing wire stunts. You pull
those moves out while you're filming, too?
jpnChrName: ハッ、ワイヤーアクションさながらだな。 いや、元から使ってなかったか？
jpnSearchText:
ハッ、ワイヤーアクションさながらだな。
いや、元から使ってなかったか？

engChrName: F-Filming? I-I haven't a clue what you're talking about.
engSearchText:
F-Filming? I-I haven't a clue what you're
talking about.
jpnChrName: な、なんのことかしら？
jpnSearchText: な、なんのことかしら？

engChrName: A-Ahaha...
engSearchText: A-Ahaha...
jpnChrName: あ、あはは……
jpnSearchText: あ、あはは……

engChrName: Everyone—if I may redirect your attention.
engSearchText: Everyone—if I may redirect your attention.
jpnChrName: ！　皆様、あそこを。
jpnSearchText: ！　皆様、あそこを。

engChrName: It's a keycard.
engSearchText: It's a keycard.
jpnChrName: こいつは……カードキーか。
jpnSearchText: こいつは……カードキーか。

engChrName: Could that be what we were looking for?!
engSearchText: Could that be what we were looking for?!
jpnChrName: もしかして……！
jpnSearchText: もしかして……！

engChrName: Yes. I imagine it's the one needed to go to the top floor.
engSearchText:
Yes. I imagine it's the one needed to go to the
top floor.
jpnChrName: はい、おそらく最上階に行くための……
jpnSearchText: はい、おそらく最上階に行くための……

engChrName: Perfect. Then as soon as we're ready, let's head on up there!
engSearchText:
Perfect. Then as soon as we're ready, let's head on
up there!
jpnChrName: ハッ、おあつらえ向きだな。 準備が出来次第乗り込むぞ！
jpnSearchText:
ハッ、おあつらえ向きだな。
準備が出来次第乗り込むぞ！

engChrName: You unlocked the elevator.
engSearchText: You unlocked the elevator.
jpnChrName: エレベーターのセキュリティロックを解除した。
jpnSearchText: <C1>エレベーターのセキュリティロックを解除した。

engChrName: Ride the elevator?
engSearchText: Ride the elevator?
jpnChrName: エレベーターを使用しますか？
jpnSearchText: <C1>エレベーターを使用しますか？

engChrName: Ride the elevator?
engSearchText: Ride the elevator?
jpnChrName: エレベーターを使用しますか？
jpnSearchText: <C1>エレベーターを使用しますか？

engChrName: Ride the elevator?
engSearchText: Ride the elevator?
jpnChrName: エレベーターを使用しますか？
jpnSearchText: <C1>エレベーターを使用しますか？

engChrName: Ride the elevator?
engSearchText: Ride the elevator?
jpnChrName: エレベーターを使用しますか？
jpnSearchText: <C1>エレベーターを使用しますか？

engChrName: Ride the elevator?
engSearchText: Ride the elevator?
jpnChrName: エレベーターを使用しますか？
jpnSearchText: <C1>エレベーターを使用しますか？

engChrName: Ride the elevator?
engSearchText: Ride the elevator?
jpnChrName: エレベーターを使用しますか？
jpnSearchText: <C1>エレベーターを使用しますか？
